{"iti51:0.1":"Itivuttaka 51 ","iti51:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti51:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti51:0.4":"Dhatusutta ","iti51:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti51:2.1":"“Tisso ima, bhikkhave, dhatuyo. ","iti51:2.2":"Katama tisso? ","iti51:2.3":"Rupadhatu, arupadhatu, nirodhadhatu—","iti51:2.4":"ima kho, bhikkhave, tisso dhatuyo”ti. ","iti51:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti51:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti51:3.1":"“Rupadhatum parinnaya, ","iti51:3.2":"aruppesu asanthita; ","iti51:3.3":"Nirodhe ye vimuccanti, ","iti51:3.4":"te jana maccuhayino. ","iti51:4.1":"Kayena amatam dhatum, ","iti51:4.2":"phusayitva nirupadhim; ","iti51:4.3":"Upadhippatinissaggam, ","iti51:4.4":"sacchikatva anasavo; ","iti51:4.5":"Deseti sammasambuddho, ","iti51:4.6":"asokam virajam padan”ti. ","iti51:5.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti51:5.2":"Dutiyam. "}